Recorded once by 
<bibRefCitation author="Bagnall" box="[548,886,1380,1406]" pageId="8" pageNumber="23" refString="Bagnall, R. S. &amp; Harrison, J. W. H. (1928) A Catalogue of the British Eriophyidae. Annals and Magazine of Natural History, 10 (2), 427 - 445." type="journal article" year="1928">
